<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN296">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>vēmpuciṉai yoṭippavuṅ kāñci pāṭavu</l>
<l>neyyuṭaik kaiya raiyavi pukaippavu</l>
<l>mellā maṉaiyuṅ kalleṉ ṟaṉavē</l>
<l>vēntuṭaṉ ṟeṟivāṉ kollō</l>
<l>neṭituvan taṉṟā ṉeṭuntakai tērē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>As they break Neem branches, sing the Kāñci</l>
<l>and fumigate with white mustard, their hands oily,</l>
<l>all the houses were noisy.</l>
<l>Will the king in [his] anger attack [them]?</l>
<l>A long [time later] it has come, the chariot of the paragon.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
